[
    {
        "text": "The idea of making a big deal of revisiting an experience in memory...",
        "startTime": 51,
        "endTime": 4521,
        "slowStartTime": 226,
        "slowEndTime": 7006
    },
    {
        "text": "...sounds a little strange or simply sad.",
        "startTime": 4868,
        "endTime": 7728,
        "slowStartTime": 7452,
        "slowEndTime": 11817
    },
    {
        "text": "We are not assiduous or devoted cultivators of our past experiences.",
        "startTime": 8348,
        "endTime": 12679,
        "slowStartTime": 12672,
        "slowEndTime": 19244
    },
    {
        "text": "We shove all the nice things that have happened to us...",
        "startTime": 12963,
        "endTime": 14977,
        "slowStartTime": 19594,
        "slowEndTime": 22691
    },
    {
        "text": "...at the back of the cupboard of our minds...",
        "startTime": 15089,
        "endTime": 16667,
        "slowStartTime": 22783,
        "slowEndTime": 25226
    },
    {
        "text": "...and don't particularly expect to see them ever again.",
        "startTime": 16981,
        "endTime": 19903,
        "slowStartTime": 25621,
        "slowEndTime": 30079
    },
    {
        "text": "They happen, and then we're done with them.",
        "startTime": 20173,
        "endTime": 22661,
        "slowStartTime": 30409,
        "slowEndTime": 34217
    },
    {
        "text": "They do sometimes come back to us, unbidden.",
        "startTime": 23107,
        "endTime": 25348,
        "slowStartTime": 34811,
        "slowEndTime": 38247
    },
    {
        "text": "We may be on a boring train ride to work...",
        "startTime": 25803,
        "endTime": 27858,
        "slowStartTime": 38854,
        "slowEndTime": 42012
    },
    {
        "text": "...and suddenly, an image of a beach at dusk comes to life.",
        "startTime": 28025,
        "endTime": 31165,
        "slowStartTime": 42188,
        "slowEndTime": 46972
    },
    {
        "text": "Or, while we're having a bath...",
        "startTime": 31548,
        "endTime": 33011,
        "slowStartTime": 47472,
        "slowEndTime": 49742
    },
    {
        "text": "...we remember climbing a flower-covered mountain with a friend a decade before.",
        "startTime": 33226,
        "endTime": 37077,
        "slowStartTime": 49989,
        "slowEndTime": 55840
    },
    {
        "text": "But little attention tends to get paid to such moments.",
        "startTime": 37677,
        "endTime": 40483,
        "slowStartTime": 56666,
        "slowEndTime": 60949
    },
    {
        "text": "We don't engineer regular encounters with them.",
        "startTime": 40827,
        "endTime": 43593,
        "slowStartTime": 61391,
        "slowEndTime": 65614
    },
    {
        "text": "We may feel we have to dismiss them as daydreaming or thinking about nothing.",
        "startTime": 44073,
        "endTime": 48172,
        "slowStartTime": 66260,
        "slowEndTime": 72483
    },
    {
        "text": "But what if we were to alter the hierarchy of prestige a little,...",
        "startTime": 48813,
        "endTime": 51982,
        "slowStartTime": 73369,
        "slowEndTime": 78198
    },
    {
        "text": "...and argue that regular immersion in our memories...",
        "startTime": 52307,
        "endTime": 55012,
        "slowStartTime": 78610,
        "slowEndTime": 82743
    },
    {
        "text": "...is a critical part of what can sustain and console us.",
        "startTime": 55287,
        "endTime": 58365,
        "slowStartTime": 83081,
        "slowEndTime": 87772
    },
    {
        "text": "And not least, is perhaps the cheapest and most flexible form of entertainment.",
        "startTime": 58686,
        "endTime": 63105,
        "slowStartTime": 88179,
        "slowEndTime": 94883
    },
    {
        "text": "We should learn, regularly, to travel around our minds...",
        "startTime": 63779,
        "endTime": 66701,
        "slowStartTime": 95818,
        "slowEndTime": 100277
    },
    {
        "text": "...and think it almost as prestigious to sit at home and reflect on a trip...",
        "startTime": 66927,
        "endTime": 70623,
        "slowStartTime": 100541,
        "slowEndTime": 106160
    },
    {
        "text": "...we once took to an island as to trek to this island encased in our cumbersome bodies.",
        "startTime": 70875,
        "endTime": 76243,
        "slowStartTime": 106462,
        "slowEndTime": 114589
    }
]